query: SELECT p.countryId, p.serviceId, p.ourPrice, s.name as service_name, c.name as country_name FROM prices p JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id WHERE s.smshubCode = 'wa'
